                                                       "Speak", "Ceris",
                                                       "Okay, now, obviously, you're going to face some {i}actual{/i} obstacles as you gather those keys, 'cause me and my sisters aren't just going to stand around and let you win. So you're going to want to avoid us as much as possible.",
