                                                       "Speak", "Ceris",
                                                       "Of course, you can always fight us if you're trapped or feeling daring, but keep in mind we're only going to get stronger any time you beat us or escape a battle with us. So don't press your luck or you're going to end up on your back and ridden into the ground.",
                                                       "ChangeImageLayer", "Expression", "Ceris", "Smile",
